    <p class="dek">New surveys show a surprising decline in the Russian president’s popularity. The pandemic will accelerate a trend of mistrust in the Kremlin.</p>
</div>
<div class="meta-data -excerpt">
        <a
        href="https://foreignpolicy.com/category/analysis/argument/"
        class="department-name -excerpt">
        Argument    </a>
        <span class="separator">|</span>
        <address class="author-list -excerpt">
    <a
        href="https://foreignpolicy.com/author/maria-snegovaya/"
        rel="author"
        class="author">
    Maria Snegovaya</a><span class="separator">,</span> <a
        href="https://foreignpolicy.com/author/denis-volkov/"
        rel="author"
        class="author">
    Denis Volkov</a><span class="separator">,</span> <a
        href="https://foreignpolicy.com/author/stepan-goncharov/"
        rel="author"
        class="author">
    Stepan Goncharov</a></address>

